headline.main: SOVIET REBUFFS SWEDEN; Declares Iron Ship Was Not Sunk by a Russian Submarine

abstract: USSR rejects Swedish protest on SS Ada Gorthon sinking; denies USSR submarine sank ship; orders naval forces to avoid Swedish territorial waters
